as a retiree was November 1, 2021; throughout his career,
HJR77 Enrolled
85 CSM Harkey exemplified the highest standards of leadership,
86 professionalism, and personal courage, earning the respect
87 and admiration of officers, noncommissioned officers, and
88 enlisted soldiers alike; now therefore,
89 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, BOTH
90 HOUSES THEREOF CONCURRING, That we hereby most highly
91 commend U.S. Army Command Sergeant Major Kevin D. Harkey for
92 his exceptional service, outstanding leadership, and lasting
93 contributions to the United States Army and our nation.
94 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, That this resolution be
95 entered into the official record as a testament to Command
96 Sergeant Major Harkey's honorable service and presented to
97 him as an expression of profound gratitude and highest
98 esteem.
